45:31.854 --> 45:32.896
Forty years.

45:33.648 --> 45:36.108
I really think you can learn something from it.

45:36.192 --> 45:37.442
I want you to soak it in.

45:43.157 --> 45:45.867
Oh, and, by the way, we did
just move into the red zone.

46:02.009 --> 46:04.010
Hey, Felix, the algorithm is solid,

46:04.095 --> 46:05.637
