two sides to every story.

49:09.196 --> 49:10.572
Oh, Jesus Christ!

49:10.656 --> 49:13.033
Ronny, you followed him to the massage parlor?

49:13.284 --> 49:16.036
(STAMMERS) Well, no, I just wanted
to call and let you know

49:16.120 --> 49:18.163
