you go home tonight, honey.

49:49.862 --> 49:51.738
Because I'm definitely going to talk to him!

49:51.822 --> 49:53.823
Okay, just take a breath.

49:54.075 --> 49:55.116
(SIGHS)

49:55.201 --> 49:58.370
