01:03:28.180 --> 01:03:30.681
I don't want to see you in front of my place.

01:03:30.765 --> 01:03:32.224
BOY: Whatever, man.

01:03:32.309 --> 01:03:33.893
Get out of here.

01:03:44.279 --> 01:03:46.780
Hi, Sepia, on Jefferson.

